Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家這麼晚還在外面遊蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  必須得懲罰一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使不是已經不會傷害我們了的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏是不會對毫無抵抗的我們進行攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游離子  我們要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  以半圓形圍住她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行集中攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.74,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是你這傢伙在發號施令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被distortion擋開  也不要停下攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.05,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快閃開  由理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏她不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼深的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是致命傷也會很快好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的傢伙居然有兩個  到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界什麼時候變得這麼莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是有緣由的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得天使領域入侵作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她的電腦裡不是有一個開發技能的軟體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡面有幾個從未見過的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是其中一個叫「harmonics」的技能發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個什麼樣的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時沒看畫面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是把一個身體分裂成兩個的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說這也是天使自己用軟體開發的技能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺並非是完全相同的兩個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這傢伙不同  很好戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏她只使用保護自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用刀刃時也一樣  只是為了擋住子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們這群廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學除外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為笨蛋基本都聚集在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我告訴你們其中一個可能性好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設那個分身的產生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在擁有強烈的攻擊意志的時候的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說分身一直遵從著當時本體的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  奏不可能擁有強烈的攻擊意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這無所謂  不過你好像很護著她嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為  她很可憐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  現在的問題是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天使的分身戰鬥的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是消除方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.37,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙在幹什麼  快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果分身是因為她的意志而產生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也應該能用她的意志來消除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要等她醒來不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  如果能用意志消除的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她還會躺在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是無意識下的產物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以連她也無法消除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算同歸於盡也只好拼命上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不會消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈不是要一直在這個世界存在下去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在放過了我們  但明天開始應該不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦偏離規範行為  恐怕會立刻和昨天一樣變成一場血戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  因為她完全繼承了約束我們的那份意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上生性好戰  糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想反抗也沒有時間去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些時間要怎樣去爭取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上課  並裝作聽課的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能去聽老師講課的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真上課的話就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不被分身發現的情況下幹別的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且堅持一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望下次再見的時候  不要少了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:01.39,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}女生宿舍  天使領域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我知道可以分身啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒辦法讓另一個消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel  Player...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟體的使用手冊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  這麼厚一本還全是英語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就沒什麼時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跳高了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是距離嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是連上這個指令就會自動消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它的發動條件是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆把整個電腦都破壞掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡嗎  那分身就不會消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  直接改寫成我能明白的程式算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間限制是10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10秒鐘要等起來還真是漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就不能設置到10秒以下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「howling」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是分身做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要刪除掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  都做得這麼周密了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須盡可能少修改一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只要她再使用一次「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「absorb」這個技能就會發動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就會回到本體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏和我約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會和我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做過那種約定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副凌亂的樣子肯定是被綁走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改寫了程式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她再使用一次那個力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加能力就會發動  分身就應該會回到本體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事也能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨陣磨槍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是敵人的行動比預想的還快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被藏起來的話就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要一邊躲避兇惡的天使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是假裝上課就已經夠麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻到底能撐多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻是說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是為了什麼加入GDM的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為崇拜岩澤同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GDM可是為了佯攻而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  面對那麼可怕的對手怎麼佯攻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你佯攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡我可是你的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼反倒是你發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩嗎  真是對不起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  雖然在演唱會中可能會尿褲子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不會退縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份決心先謝謝你了  不過現在還不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先去做力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集目擊到天使的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey  yo!  Check  this  out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a moonwalk, it's a moonwalk... Headspin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛收集來的情報看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚禁的場所很可能是在Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  一定是在那最底層
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個爆破掉的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  陷阱也還開啟著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最為危險  距離這裡最遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要潛入這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次可幾乎是全滅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一個死的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大家我即使尿褲子也會繼續唱下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現出自己的毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對那種對手  佯攻也是等著被秒殺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不需要佯攻  堂堂正正地去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要兼顧和天使的戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰內容是空降至Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其最底層順利奪回天使的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.98,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的陷阱擱著沒人管  真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…在這裡碰上天使的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是會尿褲子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請有所謂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請有所謂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有手槍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「distortion」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會比預想的更快搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是敵人又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣  那傢伙又是第一個被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後的要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想這個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先對付眼前的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您似乎很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游離子  快沒子彈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去封住路口  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能趕上的人就留下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:19.39,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼凶暴的天使居然有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比上次空降作戰的處境還要糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會出現第二個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身都使出「handsonic」和「distortion」了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說「harmonics」也能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是一群低能兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學除外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來總結問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是究竟製造了多少個分身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果分身能製造分身的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那數量就沒有限制了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那別說是兩個了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十個…二十個  說不定還有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由理已經追加過技能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身是會回到本體的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要等她們消失不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是第二個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那能力追加以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就已經量產了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚民們  終於注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學是高貴的貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她知道我們會潛入這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把已經量產了的分身佈置在這個Guild的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,trap
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後已經有兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這前方…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聚集了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說被困在這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連武器也沒法補給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是等著被幹掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出這種事到底有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就結果而言是讓我們完全服從吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們老老實實地消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個把我們一網打盡的絕妙作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.05,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B10
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再…浪費子彈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下五段！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  趁我還有意識的時候快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這種好像只有在臨死時才是條好漢的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  趁現在快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐住啊  松下五段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓松下君白白犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:04.39,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B11
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托他的福我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要前進那是最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為天使身體比較小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要封住她的動作的話  那樣做是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管天使有多麼大的力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔道的固技對她都會有效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下君教我們的柔道終於有實用的一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說對付一個天使只要犧牲一個人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後只要我們能救出本體  他們也都能獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.51,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B12
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's  my  turn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get  chance  and  luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什麼啊  這種像少年漫畫最終回一樣的劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了  繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現這身肌肉的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  去意識到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一名小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  在那片黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個神情很寂寞的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來讓你露出笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是壞透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無同學  不是的  請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是善意的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個由我去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  誰來說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我連他名字都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:18:00.00,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B15
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第幾個了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  早就沒在數了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要前進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去的話就給我快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是喜歡他還是討厭他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guild被爆破後的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:35.30,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild最底層  爆炸中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡能一口氣下到最底層
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無君和由依去找本體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦找到  就催促她使用「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向君不是也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她等著的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了  根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請提一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這如果是最後一次作戰就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  由依呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽到一聲很短暫的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了天使的犧牲品了嗎  太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是馬上就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次活下來的又只有我們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和上次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該是最後一個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你別在這裡發呆了  快點去找本體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摀住耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「howling」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有暈過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我塞著耳塞聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你就死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話  就用另一把匕首割破你的喉嚨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰線的大家都拼上了性命來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點勉強你很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是希望你能使用一個能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你用了大家就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體能受得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只用一次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好像改寫了程式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  一切都會回到她的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多冷酷的我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是分身也有意識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是同化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊你們的眾多的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到她的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次性吸收這麼多的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得會沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
